[I] Parsing gigabytes of JSON per second

[T] The simdjson library uses commonly available SIMD instructions and
[T] microparallel algorithms to parse JSON 4x faster than RapidJSON and 25x
[T] faster than JSON for Modern C++.

[U] https://simdjson.org/

